---
title: Fragrant Lamb Noodle Stir-Fry with Mushrooms, Carrot and Lime
description: A fast favourite, stir-frying is the perfect method to build flavour and cook quickly! This Fragrant Lamb Noodle Stir-Fry is spiced with lemongrass and Indonesian spices. It's perfect for a balanced lifestyle too.
